title: Channel Fish Processing Co., Inc. Recalls Siluriformes Fish Products Due to Misbranding and Undeclared Allergens
summary: EDITORS NOTE: This release is being updated to add a date code missing from a product included in the recall release issued June 16, 2017. WASHINGTON, June 16, 2017 Channel Fish Processing Co., Inc, a Boston, Mass. establishment, is recalling approximately 840 pounds of breaded...
